reviewText: Our old friend Arthur Franz was in this movie, one of his first before his longtime career in TV and after he came home from serving in B-24 bombers in WW 2.

Thank you for making these available.

I have not watched the whole film yet , but I am writing this review to let those know that the 1st release of this  film by Mr. Fat o9is not supposed to be on the market anymore.  the red white and black cover was released on 2012-2101 and is extremely poor in print quality and is not worth a buck. So be careful not to buy this print even though the later release  is a couple of more dollars.
